item.title: [[PI]] 2 Errors PLease help?
item.dc:creator: @Ashi Ashi
item.description:
@Ashi wrote:

Step 1) Open client.java with notepad
Step 2) Press ctrl + g on your keyboard then type 120 and press enter
Step 3) You should now see a line saying “public void models() {” replace that with “public void models2() {” (without quotes)
Step 4) Press ctrl + g on your keyboard then type 129 and press enter
Step 5) You should now see a line saying “public byte[] getModel(int index) {” replace that with public byte[] getModel2(int index) {"
Step 6) Compile your server with the compiler.bat or build.bat

Enjoy

(it’s noob friendly!)
